\c 8
\s Kristu mupristi mukuru wesungano itsva
\p
\v 1 Zvino shoko guru pazvinhu zvatataura \add ndirori\add*: Tine mupristi mukuru wakadai wakagara kuruoko rwerudyi rwechigaro cheushe cheMukuru kumatenga,
\v 2 mushumiri wenzvimbo tsvene, newetabhenakeri yechokwadi Ishe yaakadzika, kwete munhu.
\v 3 nokuti mupristi mukuru umwe neumwe wakagadzirwa kubaira zvipo nezvibairo; naizvozvo zvakafanira kuti naye ave nechimwe chaangabaira.
\v 4 nokuti kana aiva panyika, ungadai asina kutombova mupristi, vapristi zvavaripo, vanobaira zvipo zvinoenderana nemurairo;
\v 5 vanoshumira zviratidzo nemumvuri wezvinhu zvekudenga, Mozisi sezvaakarairwa naMwari oda kugadzira tabhenakeri; nokuti wakati: Chenjera kuti uite zvese zvichienderana nemufananidzo wawakaratidzwa mugomo.
\v 6 Asi ikozvino wakawana ushumiri hwakanyanyisa kunaka, sezvaariwo murevereri wesungano inopfuura pakunaka, yakasimbiswa pazvivimbiso zvinopfuura pakunaka.
\v 7 nokuti dai iya yekutanga yakange isina chaingapomerwa, dai pasina nzvimbo yakatsvakirwa yechipiri.
\v 8 nokuti achivapa mhosva, unoti: Tarira, mazuva anouya, unotaura Ishe, zvino ndichaita sungano itsva neimba yaIsraeri uye neimba yaJudha.
\v 9 Kwete zvichienderana nesungano yandakaita nemadzibaba avo, pazuva randakabata ruoko rwavo kuti ndivabudise munyika yeEgipita; nokuti havana kurambira musungano yangu, neni ndikasava nehanya navo, unoreva Ishe;
\v 10 nokuti iyi isungano yandichasungana nayo neimba yaIsraeri shure kwemazuva iwayo, unotaura Ishe; ndichaisa mirairo yangu mumurangariro wavo, nemuhana dzavo ndichainyora; uye ndichava kwavari Mwari, ivo vachavawo kwandiri vanhu;
\v 11 uye havangatongozodzidzisi umwe neumwe umwe wake, neumwe neumwe hama yake, achiti: Ziva Ishe; nokuti vose vachandiziva, kubva kumuduku wavo kusvikira kumukuru wavo.
\v 12 Nokuti ndichava netsitsi pakusarurama kwavo, nezvivi zvavo nezvakaipa zvavo handichatongozorangariri.
\v 13 Pakuti: \add Sungano\add* itsva, yakasakadza yekutanga. Zvino chosakarawo chova chakare, chava pedo kurova.
